Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:13.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经在灭火中了 但还是浓烟滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,包括市政厅的整条街都成了废墟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:24.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟将火药啊 油啊一股脑地都用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:26.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是爽爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:29.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,爽你个头啊 你这放火魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:32.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明能非常顺利地进行无血政变的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:34.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,库乌爹达？给老子说日语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:38.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是日本人啊 你这狗屎日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:42.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 黑王军攻过来这件事是预料之外的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:43.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,预料之外的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:45.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是已经在能够做到的范围内努力地做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:46.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,至少称赞一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:48.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:53.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 阿丰怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:57.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一君现在正在帮他缝合伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:00:59.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏能活下来呢 那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:03.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,醒不来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:06.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已经好好地帮他缝过伤口了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:08.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是缝合伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:11.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说更像是把用剩的布料缝在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:15.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:20.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边世界的时候也是伤痕累累的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.57,0:01:26.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样活 才能像他这样活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:36.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了阿丰 事情都进展得非常顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:39.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那名敌将往这边来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:42.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,事情应该会很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:46.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快阻止他啊 那孩子迟早会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:47.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他是总大将吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:50.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,挡也挡不住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是那种武士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:56.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,挡也挡不住 是绝对阻止不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:58.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是父母也阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是君主也阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:05.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙原本所在的岛津家就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:09.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙肯顺从的话 我该多轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道三国志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:16.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦 老子可是信长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:20.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在的立场好像是军师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:21.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:25.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你虽然想做得像孔明或者周瑜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但你现在更像是陈宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要像陈宫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,会死吧 最后会死的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:34.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给我向吕布道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:37.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 三国志的人物最后全都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:42.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么以后要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:46.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 无血占领失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:49.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,首都不仅被烧毁了 市政厅也成废墟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:53.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,各地的军队也不会乖乖地归顺我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:57.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王攻过来的目的应该就是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,各地的军队都会在自己的领地内进行军阀化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们应该会独立割据 群雄割据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我对消除群雄割据这种情况可是非常擅长的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:13.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为以前我用天下布武解决过类似的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,---op---
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,北壁有什么动静吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只能知道好像在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但具体在做什么就完全不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:01.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 就这样下去会没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:05.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我按你说的将两名斥候的装备带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要去北壁内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 我独自一人潜入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不这样的话发生了什么也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,师徒都爱这么乱来呢「十月机关」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,做道士还真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,数量好多 这个规模完全就是城市啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,小声点 被发现就全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,头脑好像要出问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物们居然在做买卖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在使用像是货币一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:01.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是铜币吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是在哪里拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,青铜龙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:31.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「活着的铜矿山」么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没见过如此有活力的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕比起因战争而疲惫的各王国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,除古宾嫩以外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可能就是大陆上最繁盛的城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:47.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原本在北壁的卡尔阿迪斯的人们现在怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被杀光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:06.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我们人类 奴隶制在每个国家都是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:09.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,从古至今的每个国家 甚至到现在也都还存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:11.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和这些家伙有着决定性的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:23.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不会吃奴隶的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是奴隶 是家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这和我们对家畜做的事情一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,买卖家畜 让它们搬运东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不能工作了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就吃掉 人类的家畜化么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:49.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一开始也只是去抓原野的马群和羊群而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:53.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,它们这个情况则是畜产和奴隶制同时发展
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:08:00.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,文明化的进程怎么可能进行得这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:05.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不久之前连农耕都做不到的兽人和哥布林们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:09.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如今却连文字 货币经济 劳役奴隶制都学懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是人类用数十年 数百年才发展起来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:17.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有黑王和废弃物这些教师在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这些作为学生的兽人和哥布林真的学得懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:25.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,难道有什么在影响着这些被称作怪物的生命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:30.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你们在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道哪个国家的间谍？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又或是「十月机关」那些家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,胆子挺肥的嘛 你俩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉 但先拔刀的可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,多 多古
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:08.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是十月机关 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经全部见识到了 废弃物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全部？你真爱开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:20.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真正应该见识的东西在墙壁的另一边哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:47.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,废弃物会和那些怪物一起向人类进军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也因为久违的战事 现在跃跃欲试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:53.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,事先告诉你 我可是很强的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:57.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要平家那样 轻易就被灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:00.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受七颠八倒的败北吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:05.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不是狗头人和哥布林那种程度的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是人类和怪物之间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:10.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上一切的生存竞争了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有废弃物在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:20.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能统一种类 语言 生态都不同的怪物们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:25.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,企图让漂流者统帅种族 文化 语言都不同的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,集结统一的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:32.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们「十月机关」的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:36.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这边要做的事情对方肯定不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:40.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这边做得到的事情对方肯定做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是学者般傲慢的思考方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:47.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王比你们更快做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然的 毕竟他已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:53.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在成为他们的救世主这件事上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:57.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:02.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在历史上伟大的王有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,睿智的学者数都数不完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只有「他」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:10.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只有「他」是万中无一的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:14.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现身吧 安倍晴明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:21.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算藏在弟子的影子里看多久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:36.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不拯救世人的救世主 并非救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是无用 有害之人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个世界只当成人的物品来考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是公务学者的傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:49.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我像你不同 对人感觉不到丝毫的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的可能性可是无限大的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会饶恕想要毁灭世界的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要灭亡的是人世而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:03.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人类被灭亡然后由新的生命来接手这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:07.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是世代交替这种事情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了人类的可能性对吧「十月」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:15.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那份可能性也是不可饶恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:18.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人类太过聪明了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:23.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者带来了火枪 制作出了火药
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算他们不把东西带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:30.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,几百年后 这个世界的人类也会擅自制造出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就算漂流者离去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:37.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也会对铁进行改良 对火药进行改良
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:42.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后会用着更加先进的武器杀掉几百万 几千万的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者下次会带着什么出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人类还会生产出什么样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把整个城市都吹飞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,产出灭绝生命的传染病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭这颗星球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:59.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人类只会连累其他生命一同奔赴死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人类简直难以救药…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:01.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是无可救药的疯狂的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:08.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要让过于聪明的人类灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:11.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后制造出不会像人类那样做的生命接手这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:13.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的救世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:16.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我会杀掉人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,加速人类的灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:21.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我会杀死漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:22.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这些自相矛盾的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:25.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的那些怪物又是怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:29.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们把商业和农业教给了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:33.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一样的 就算他们接手了这个世代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:37.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很久之后 也会诞生出枪 火药也会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:41.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,假如就算人类会像你所说的道路前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:45.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在所做的事情不也会走向相同的道路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:51.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,技术和文明也有一步都没有前进的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说变得更加落后了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:58.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在罗马 希腊产生的技术和知识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,后来的世人完全不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:06.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为制作方法完全搞不懂就称其为「由恶魔所制造的」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:11.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很久之前的希腊就已经清楚地球是圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:14.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,后来的世人却认为整片大地都是平的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:18.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说地球围绕着太阳转的人被审判了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:23.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,革新者被杀掉 有异议者闭口不谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那段时期便被称作暗黑时代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要一个为什么要这样做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂吗「十月」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在「那边」行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:38.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在「这边」就可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不得不做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我所要创造的不会被灭绝的恐怖所困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:46.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这颗星球不会被玷污的安宁的摇篮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:51.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,永久持续下去的美好的暗黑时代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:57.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,故此我的名字就叫做「黑王」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:09.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王那家伙 真能说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:11.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1566,543)}活该
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:11.96,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1566,689)}活该
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:24.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王 你必须被打败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:28.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是对墙壁这边的生命来说还是对面的生命来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:32.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别小瞧人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人类可是很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:37.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是可以凭借自己的力量打破你所束缚的未来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,符咒术么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在用着很有趣的术嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会小看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:56.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我会全心全意地灭亡人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我都跟你说过多少次不能乱动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:07.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:15.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,总是像那样战斗的话会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:19.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道除此以外的战斗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:26.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,十三岁开始除了战斗以外的事情都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我除了战斗以外什么都不会做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:37.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我觉得这样也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:40.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这样死去也很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能死哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,阿丰你死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:47.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大概肯定全部的齿轮都会坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:51.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信 老爷爷 人妖 精灵 矮人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都会坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然阿丰你没有自觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家原来评议会的那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,资产全部没收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,国库的钱也一点都不剩地给我拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:10.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,总之现在要钱 钱不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱相当于没有睾丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,值钱的东西全都没收然后低价卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:22.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,积累了五十年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你也给我大把大把交出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 请你把这想成是投资
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,换做我的话就会很高兴地让出全财产
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:36.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,顺利的话也许可以完全经营整个国家哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:41.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧来吧 完事之后多少都能取回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你来不来投资啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:48.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这桩好事我现在只和你一个人谈过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对没有损失啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:53.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对绝对 绝对绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人要被忽悠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:58.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这和说好的不同啊 圣日尔曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会没收财产
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说过会保障我们的地位和资产吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:05.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这种程度就可以完事了你们就应该给我感激涕零
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要是以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:10.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是会叛你们割睾丸的逆磔之刑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:10.86,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,逆磔之刑:古人将人绑在柱子上刺死的刑罚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔曼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:13.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别给我说不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被骗了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:20.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,头脑很好但精神状态却还是小孩子 真是恼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个胡子眼带也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:26.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那码事归那码事 人妖 我有事情想让你做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:28.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,窃窃私语 窃窃私语
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:31.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 拜托别人做事就这么爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要求还这么离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:36.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜托别人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:40.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只会拜托那些有能力做这件事的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「和古宾嫩的和平」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:48.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很擅长激发别人的干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:53.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是当务之急是得应付奥尔特各地的地方军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,西方的第三军 第四军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:01.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是奥尔特的重心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:04.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,海岸线的第五军已经是大海的藻屑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:09.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里北方的第二军如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,军队的规模不小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:14.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的情况挺不可思议的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:17.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,北方第二军应该在和北方的亚人种…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这种说法已经不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:22.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在和犬人和猫人的各个部族进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:28.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那些部族突然变得很凶暴 攻势变得很猛烈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:32.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,连这边的情况都不清楚还来请求援助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:35.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:38.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是黑王军？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:44.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,上 打爆他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么两翼开始向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么中央开始往后退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 打信号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:07.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 伏兵出击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:11.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 上 干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:13.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人都是那个样子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他的吗 像他这种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:21.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个符条拿给我真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真是让人摸不着头脑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然踢我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:26.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,踢了你么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是罗马的救国英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙居然真的踢了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 外国人 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在唧唧歪歪什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦 只是觉得你很厉害而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,况且日本是哪里啊 那种国家才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是哪里的外国人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:48.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一整副西部剧的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是美国佬的话就踢你 是英国佬的话也踢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,玻利维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:58.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是玻利维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道美国是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:03.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 耶 玻利维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:06.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪里啊 玻利维亚 才没有那种国家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,空神大人 敌人被追得走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打爆他们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你们这么精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:17.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不把我带走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,晴明说让你在这里加油干
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会再来的所以加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 西庇阿 要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:32.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去把敌人打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:35.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 把我带走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:37.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真想回罗马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}吵死了 笨蛋家伙 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:41.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,头 头被勒住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:46.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我又感觉我的战术被抄袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,罗马去死吧 罗马去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:53.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}西庇阿去死吧 加图去死吧　鸟尾蛤活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:51.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:53.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不会来抢你东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:56.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}这是西庇阿的捣的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:58.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,终于坏掉了么？这个老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:02.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个老爷子 偶尔很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:03.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.64,0:22:05.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信先生 信先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在首都有权势的人已经过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在大厅集合了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 来了么 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来给他们一个下马威吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:18.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要进行施政演说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:21.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把当地的这些家伙一口气镇住然后占据整个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:24.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有事情能比这更让我愉悦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:27.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我去稍微表演一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:29.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微把耳朵靠过来 欧派和人妖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是奥尔米
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:31.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讨厌 怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:32.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,事情变得很严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:35.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到漂流者再次出现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:37.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}听说袭击过来的黑色的军队是怪物组成的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:38.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:44.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即将开始由从天而降的我们的新的支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:50.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主漂流者大人向各位赐言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:53.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那是圣日尔曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:56.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,旁边的是十月机关的道士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.99,0:23:00.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,出现新漂流者的传闻原来是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.49,0:23:08.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有请代表漂流者的第六天魔王织田信长大人出场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:09.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:12.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经怎么样都好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:26.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我正是第六天魔王 织田前右府信长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:33.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我代表我们的主人「鬼岛津」丰久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:36.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有事情向你们宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:41.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕了 害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:44.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 漂流者大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:45.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我第六天魔王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第六天不知道什么大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:53.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的那位就是丰久大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:58.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:00.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:01.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:02.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.31,0:24:04.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一 与一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:06.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰又出来走动了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:10.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个 那个可怕人就是你们的主人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:13.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,额 嗯 对 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:15.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个奇怪的鬼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.29,0:24:20.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 虽然的确让他们害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:22.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但这不是完全冷场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.47,0:24:27.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}饭 饭 饭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.10,0:24:26.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,与一 快点对那家伙做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.91,0:24:29.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的能赢黑王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.68,0:24:32.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.21,0:24:34.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你什么都没想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.22,0:24:35.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔米派
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.26,0:24:37.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快展现你的胸部来转移焦点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.94,0:24:39.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻啊你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,---ed---
