Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:29.74,difters-op,,0,0,0,,踩下油门 奏响福音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:30.45,difters-op,,0,0,0,,歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:30.45,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,72.6)\fs43.5}sing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:44.22,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾驰 在这蜿蜒曲折中突进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:47.14,difters-op,,0,0,0,,已欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:50.64,difters-op,,0,0,0,,这是飓风般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.81,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.19,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了这份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.65,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的飓风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:04.49,difters-op,,0,0,0,,即使已超速 也无法捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:09.24,difters-op,,0,0,0,,引擎全开 全身绷紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:09.99,difters-op,,0,0,0,,和我一同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:09.99,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,72.6)\fs43.5}everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.51,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾驰 在这蜿蜒曲折中突进
