Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:30.35,difters-op,,0,0,0,,这是飓风般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.22,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.77,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了这份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:38.15,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的飓风
