Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.59,0:25:08.55,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodthirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.59,0:25:08.55,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.72,0:25:13.51,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滾る心に刃と
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.72,0:25:13.51,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}灼热翻腾的心中之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.68,0:25:20.64,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}無に成る大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.68,0:25:20.64,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举心无旁骛的大义之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.73,0:25:32.11,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}陽炎は揺れるシンフォニー
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.73,0:25:32.11,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}热浪就如晃荡的交响乐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.32,0:25:42.12,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}その声　響く三日月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.32,0:25:42.12,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那歌声 在新月之夜下荡漾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.33,0:25:45.46,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}こんなにくべる炎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.33,0:25:45.46,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如此久久不息的火焰
